WEBVTT

00:01.555 --> 00:04.241
WOMAN:
<i>The year is 2048.</i>

00:04.275 --> 00:08.045
<i>Evolving technologies</i>
<i>can no longer be regulated.</i>

00:08.079 --> 00:10.280
<i>Dangerous advancements forever</i>

00:10.315 --> 00:12.482
<i>alter the criminal landscape.</i>

00:12.517 --> 00:14.117
<i>Police are not prepared.</i>

00:15.720 --> 00:18.322
<i>Law enforcement combats</i>
<i>this corruption</i>

00:18.356 --> 00:21.858
<i>with a new line of defense.</i>

00:21.893 --> 00:24.461
<i>But not all are created equal.</i>

00:26.497 --> 00:28.465
RUDY:
<i>The idea behind the DRNs</i>

00:28.499 --> 00:30.367
<i>was to be as human as possible.</i>

00:30.401 --> 00:32.970
<i>They were based on a program</i>
<i>called Synthetic Soul.</i>

00:33.004 --> 00:34.371
JOHN:
<i>That's one of the crazy ones.</i>

00:34.405 --> 00:36.173
- I'll lead you in?
- Let's go.

00:36.207 --> 00:39.643
WOMAN: <i>Now all cops...</i>
<i>human and manmade together...</i>

00:39.677 --> 00:43.013
<i>take on the battle</i>
<i>to watch over us all.</i>

00:43.049 --> 00:46.354
