MAN:
He's still not picking up.

01:01.933 --> 01:04.101
MAN 2: He's supposed to be
waiting for our call.

01:04.135 --> 01:06.103
There's no reason
for him not to answer.

01:06.137 --> 01:07.638
MAN:
This is not like him.

01:07.672 --> 01:10.240
