01:41.539 --> 01:44.775
Come on, man, you're gonna
hurt Nuri's feelings.

01:44.809 --> 01:46.710
He's not the one
being inconsiderate.

01:46.744 --> 01:48.979
- I already offered you one.
- I don't eat.

01:49.013 --> 01:51.214
Well, I do. You got a problem
with that, go wait in the car.

01:51.249 --> 01:53.350
Don't you know...
in Japan, it's rude to leave

01:53.384 --> 01:54.718
